metadata.name: MIKLOS #1/15
metadata.description:
"Miklos" and "Gidget" are the unique buddies created by Yusuke Hanai for the signature "The Road and the Sky Grill & Bar" inside FWEN Metaverse. 

The tokens can be redeemed via a “tap-to-own” card & chip that is included with each artwork that ties the physical artwork to a digital token.
